Who else is hiding?

305
00:24:44,869 --> 00:24:46,469
It is our Sonu's 'roka'
tomorrow.

306
00:24:46,629 --> 00:24:48,269
Let's celebrate together.

307
00:24:49,549 --> 00:24:51,229
Come on, all of you say cheers.

308
00:24:58,549 --> 00:25:00,789
Cheers!

